org.cougaar.lib.web.redirect
Interface ServletRedirectorService

All Superinterfaces:
Service, ServletRedirector
public interface ServletRedirectorService
extends ServletRedirector, Service

This service provides a ServletRedirector for infrastructure use in redirecting / tunneling servlet requests to remote agents.

For example, if node "A" contains agent "1", and a servlet request is made for agent "2", then the root servlet will invoke the redirector to locate agent "2"'s address and redirect/tunnel the client to that remote node.

See Also:
redirector API, registry for multiple redirectors in the same node.
